      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huntington%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "The 1867 arrival of the Long Island Rail Road shifted Huntington from agriculture to a thriving tourist and commuter hub.",
